India Approves Vedanta’s Cairn Stake Purchase Proposal With Conditions

-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y
-- 
2011-06-30T14:13:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/india-approves-vedanta-s-cairn-stake-purchase-proposal-with-conditions.html
India ’s Cabinet approved  Vedanta
Resources Plc (VED) ’s plan to take control of  Cairn India Ltd. (CAIR)  with
conditions, Krishna Tirath, minister for women and child
development, told reporters in  New Delhi  today. No further
information was immediately available.  To contact the reporter on this story:
